  \end{figure}
}{}

\subsection{Temporal distribution (session vs follow-up)}
Session versus follow-up comparisons per molecule appear in \Cref{tab:agg-mol-window}. As expected for acute psychedelic effects, the majority of signals concentrate in the session window, with limited persistence at follow-up.

