\subsection{Sensitivity and heterogeneity}
Where available, leave-one-out analyses did not materially alter directionality. Heterogeneity varied by molecule and AE; estimates are reported in \Cref{tab:overall-by-molecule} and \Cref{tab:agg-mol-window}. Funnel or Egger testing was only considered when $k \ge 10$.

